<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Kingsman</title>
    <!-- FONTS -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Montserrat:300,400,700" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/style.css">
  </head>
  <body>
    <!-- ====== TOP HEADER BAR ====== -->
    <div class="header">
      <!-- title -->
      <div class="header-title">
        <img src="/public/img/logo.png" alt="kingsman logo">
        <h1>KINGSMAN TAILOR</h1>
      </div>
      <!-- navigation -->
      <div class="header-nav">
        <ul>
          <% if (session) { %>
          <li>
              <a href="/room">fitting room three</a>
          </li>
          <!-- add your link to create a user here -->
          <li>
            <a href="/signup">Sign Up</a>
          </li>
          <% } 
          <!-- add your link to the log in page here -->
          if (session) { %>
          <!-- add your form button to log out here -->
          <li>
            <form action='/sessions?_method=DELETE' method="POST">
              <input type="submit" value="LOGOUT" />
            </form>
          </li>
          <% } else { %>
            <li><a href="/login">Login</a></li>
            <% } %>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- ===== MAIN SPLASH PAGE CONTENT ===== -->
    <div class="main">
      <!-- image -->
      <img src="/public/img/splash.jpg" alt="splash image of kingsman display window"/>
      <!-- about -->
      <div class="main-abt">
        <h1>the modern gentleman's armour: a suit</h1>
        As Hemingway said, "There is nothing noble in being superior to your fellow man. True nobility is being superior to your former self.""
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
